  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>Several <b>plazas</b> are described in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i>.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Named_plazas\">Named plazas</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Plaza&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Named plazas\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Plaza_of_Pride\" title=\"Plaza of Pride\">Plaza of Pride</a> (Astapor)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Plaza_of_Punishment\" title=\"Plaza of Punishment\">Plaza of Punishment</a> (Astapor)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Plaza_of_Purification\" title=\"Plaza of Purification\">Plaza of Purification</a> (Meereen)</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Unnamed_plazas\">Unnamed plazas</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Plaza&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Unnamed plazas\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li>A great plaza made of white marble in front of the Great Sept of Baelor (King's Landing)</li>\n<li>A wide marble plaza outside the Starry Sept (Oldtown)</li>\n<li>Central plaza in front of the Great Pyramid (Meereen)</li>\n<li>Plaza of the Temple of the Lord of Light (Volantis)</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404073053\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.003 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 7/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 byt